snippet.title: Mr. Shootem Breaks Out! | Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
http://shootem.biz

The Kickstarter campaign for Mr. Shootem Breaks Out! is now LIVE, from September 20 - October 20!

About Mr. Shootem Breaks Out!:

Mr. Shootem Breaks Out! is an arcade-inspired puzzle-platform-shooter about destroying levels and levels of bricks by using a ball and pure firepower! Shoot the ball, strike a pose, and LITERALLY level the playing field!

Play as a wide array of characters with their own abilities, including characters from Super Freaks, Plok, and much more!
